memories began coming up.

00:23:53.020 --> 00:23:54.700 align:middle line:84%
When he went to
the retreat leaders

00:23:54.700 --> 00:23:57.070 align:middle line:84%
and revealed his
mental health history,

00:23:57.070 --> 00:24:00.856 align:middle line:84%
they decided it was
best for him to leave.

00:24:00.856 --> 00:24:03.880 align:middle line:84%
>> The first time I went
to the Vipassana center,

00:24:03.880 --> 00:24:08.670 align:middle line:84%
I had a memory of when I was
really young and just being

00:24:08.670 --> 00:24:10.350 align:middle line:90%
in a bathroom.

00:24:10.350 --> 00:24:16.520 align:middle line:90%
It was involving a relative.

00:24:16.520 --> 00:24:18.250 align:middle line:90%
I'm just like dancing around.

00:24:18.250 --> 00:24:22.240 align:middle line:84%
I was molested as a child, and
it was involving a relative.

00:24:22.240 --> 00:24:26.160 align:middle line:90%


00:24:26.160 --> 00:24:29.120 align:middle line:84%
Once I realized my
grandfather had molested me,

00:24:29.120 --> 00:24:33.650 align:middle line:84%
I went to speak to my parents,
and they didn't believe me.

00:24:33.650 --> 00:24:39.170 align:middle line:90%


00:24:39.170 --> 00:24:40.880 align:middle line:90%
I'm losing my house.

00:24:40.880 --> 00:24:42.400 align:middle line:90%
I'm losing my job.

00:24:42.400 --> 00:24:44.980 align:middle line:84%
And I just walked away
from all my bills,

00:24:44.980 --> 00:24:47.410 align:middle line:90%
just looking into the abyss.

00:24:47.410 --> 00:24:49.810 align:middle line:84%
And that's when
I began believing

00:24:49.810 --> 00:24:54.520 align:middle line:84%
that my mother molested
me, my father molested me.

00:24:54.520 --> 00:24:56.000 align:middle line:90%
My mind just, I think--

00:24:56.000 --> 00:24:57.706 align:middle line:90%
it couldn't handle it anymore.

00:24:57.706 --> 00:25:01.354 align:middle line:90%


00:25:01.354 --> 00:25:03.670 align:middle line:10%
>> So if I have an
unusual way of feeling,

00:25:03.670 --> 00:25:06.580 align:middle line:10%
and my emotions are really
big, and having a hard time,

00:25:06.580 --> 00:25:09.280 align:middle line:10%
and the culture and my
family doesn't support that,

00:25:09.280 --> 00:25:12.290 align:middle line:10%
I can go off into a really
isolated way and become very,

00:25:12.290 --> 00:25:15.430 align:middle line:10%
very disturbed-- alienated,
isolated, more chaotic,

00:25:15.430 --> 00:25:18.226 align:middle line:10%
more rigid, and you
give me a label.

00:25:18.226 --> 00:25:19.600 align:middle line:84%
And then we look
at someone whose

00:25:19.600 --> 00:25:22.840 align:middle line:84%
"mind--" that is their feelings,
their thoughts, their behavior

00:25:22.840 --> 00:25:24.140 align:middle line:90%
is off--

00:25:24.140 --> 00:25:27.130 align:middle line:84%
and then we say, oh,
they have a bad brain.

00:25:27.130 --> 00:25:30.120 align:middle line:84%
And then either you isolate them
because you're afraid of them

00:25:30.120 --> 00:25:31.870 align:middle line:84%
or you give them pills
or whatever you do.

00:25:31.870 --> 00:25:34.330 align:middle line:84%
And medication is
sometimes essential.

00:25:34.330 --> 00:25:38.160 align:middle line:84%
But if you don't first start
with communities of support,

00:25:38.160 --> 00:25:39.610 align:middle line:84%
then of course
the brain is going

00:25:39.610 --> 00:25:42.040 align:middle line:84%
to stop functioning so
well, because the brain is

00:25:42.040 --> 00:25:42.970 align:middle line:90%
a social organ.

00:25:42.970 --> 00:25:46.910 align:middle line:90%


00:25:46.910 --> 00:25:50.480 align:middle line:84%
Relationships are just as
important as brain processes,

00:25:50.480 --> 00:25:53.120 align:middle line:84%
and I feel very
deeply that if we

00:25:53.120 --> 00:25:57.050 align:middle line:84%
could make that
clear to everyone,

00:25:57.050 --> 00:25:58.820 align:middle line:84%
we could have a shift
in how we actually

00:25:58.820 --> 00:25:59.820 align:middle line:90%
take care of each other.

00:25:59.820 --> 00:26:02.712 align:middle line:90%


00:26:02.712 --> 00:26:06.490 align:middle line:84%
>> This is myself and
my best friend Mia.

00:26:06.490 --> 00:26:10.660 align:middle line:84%
And she was a huge part
of my life-- someone

00:26:10.660 --> 00:26:11.650 align:middle line:90%
that I could trust.

00:26:11.650 --> 00:26:12.910 align:middle line:90%
And we lived together.

00:26:12.910 --> 00:26:14.170 align:middle line:90%
We moved to New York together.

00:26:14.170 --> 00:26:15.970 align:middle line:90%
>> We wrote together.

00:26:15.970 --> 00:26:17.470 align:middle line:90%
We sung together.

00:26:17.470 --> 00:26:21.580 align:middle line:84%
We managed an art
gallery together.

00:26:21.580 --> 00:26:23.020 align:middle line:90%
We created a business together.

00:26:23.020 --> 00:26:26.950 align:middle line:84%
So we were very much a
part of each other's lives.

00:26:26.950 --> 00:26:28.630 align:middle line:84%
>> During one of
my lowest points,

00:26:28.630 --> 00:26:31.810 align:middle line:84%
