what was happening.

00:26:31.810 --> 00:26:35.680 align:middle line:84%
>> When I look at her, this
is not the person that I had

00:26:35.680 --> 00:26:37.180 align:middle line:90%
originally met.

00:26:37.180 --> 00:26:40.970 align:middle line:84%
And then she was on medication
when she was in that hospital.

00:26:40.970 --> 00:26:43.060 align:middle line:90%
And it was changing her.

00:26:43.060 --> 00:26:45.700 align:middle line:84%
