00:28:47.610 --> 00:28:49.710 align:middle line:10%
differently from a peer
perspective and say,

00:28:49.710 --> 00:28:50.160 align:middle line:10%
you know what?

00:28:50.160 --> 00:28:51.060 align:middle line:90%
I've been through this.

00:28:51.060 --> 00:28:51.980 align:middle line:90%
I know where you are.

00:28:51.980 --> 00:28:53.700 align:middle line:84%
I've actually
experienced myself.

00:28:53.700 --> 00:28:55.410 align:middle line:10%
Someone that hasn't
experienced it,

00:28:55.410 --> 00:28:59.930 align:middle line:10%
it's very, very hard for
them to see through it.

00:28:59.930 --> 00:29:04.690 align:middle line:90%


00:29:04.690 --> 00:29:07.310 align:middle line:84%
>> [SINGING]
Sometimes the music--

00:29:07.310 --> 00:29:09.430 align:middle line:90%
she's just like a lover.

00:29:09.430 --> 00:29:12.790 align:middle line:90%
