00:29:40.486 --> 00:29:42.110 align:middle line:84%
We say there's
something wrong with you

00:29:42.110 --> 00:29:46.100 align:middle line:84%
instead of actually addressing
the fact that, as a society,

00:29:46.100 --> 00:29:49.365 align:middle line:84%
we don't have the skills to
be able to support somebody

00:29:49.365 --> 00:29:50.165 align:middle line:90%
like that.

00:29:50.165 --> 00:29:53.450 align:middle line:84%
>> [SINGING] --to wonder what
