missed him at all?

00:30:02.700 --> 00:30:06.618 align:middle line:90%
Oh, did she miss him at all?

00:30:06.618 --> 00:30:11.100 align:middle line:84%
>> He seems to just tune right
into what people are feeling.

00:30:11.100 --> 00:30:13.500 align:middle line:84%
I don't think he knows how
