00:30:18.270 --> 00:30:19.600 align:middle line:90%
to end up in the back of a car.

00:30:19.600 --> 00:30:23.920 align:middle line:84%
>> [SINGING] Guess
I'll never know.

00:30:23.920 --> 00:30:29.680 align:middle line:90%


00:30:29.680 --> 00:30:34.040 align:middle line:84%
>> Being here and finding
that love, and comfort,

00:30:34.040 --> 00:30:38.450 align:middle line:84%
and just the
acceptance saved me.

00:30:38.450 --> 00:30:42.590 align:middle line:84%
Without that, with just being
in your head, having nothing

00:30:42.590 --> 00:30:46.280 align:middle line:84%
other than rejection to what
you're experiencing going on

00:30:46.280 --> 00:30:49.810 align:middle line:90%
is absolutely maddening.

00:30:49.810 --> 00:30:54.410 align:middle line:10%
>> One of the problems in this
industrial society is that

00:30:54.410 --> 00:30:56.540 align:middle line:10%
the so-called normal people--

00:30:56.540 --> 00:31:00.740 align:middle line:10%
they don't want to admit that
they're psychotic, actually.

00:31:00.740 --> 00:31:02.660 align:middle line:90%
We live in a psychotic society.

00:31:02.660 --> 00:31:03.650 align:middle line:90%
I'm sorry.

00:31:03.650 --> 00:31:04.520 align:middle line:90%
We do.

00:31:04.520 --> 00:31:06.350 align:middle line:90%
And what is meant by psychotic?

00:31:06.350 --> 00:31:07.495 align:middle line:90%
Out of touch with reality.

00:31:07.495 --> 00:31:10.760 align:middle line:84%
>> When somebody who's
in this delicate state--

00:31:10.760 --> 00:31:12.410 align:middle line:90%
you know, they're in a process.

00:31:12.410 --> 00:31:14.900 align:middle line:84%
They're sent to prison,
they're sent to jail,

00:31:14.900 --> 00:31:16.530 align:middle line:84%
they're sent to a
psychiatric ward,

00:31:16.530 --> 00:31:18.117 align:middle line:84%
or they're chemically
incarcerated,

00:31:18.117 --> 00:31:18.950 align:middle line:90%
or they're homeless.

00:31:18.950 --> 00:31:20.750 align:middle line:90%
>> I'm not against medications.

00:31:20.750 --> 00:31:22.030 align:middle line:90%
I'm not against hospitals.

00:31:22.030 --> 00:31:23.030 align:middle line:90%
I'm not against doctors.

00:31:23.030 --> 00:31:26.240 align:middle line:84%
I know many people who are
benefited by medications.

00:31:26.240 --> 00:31:28.970 align:middle line:84%
But we have a one-size-fits
all framework.

00:31:28.970 --> 00:31:32.480 align:middle line:84%
We think that the
issue is biological;

00:31:32.480 --> 00:31:35.870 align:middle line:84%
the solution is medical
and pharmaceutical;

00:31:35.870 --> 00:31:38.210 align:middle line:84%
and we see it as
objective science.

00:31:38.210 --> 00:31:39.335 align:middle line:90%
It's not objective science.

00:31:39.335 --> 00:31:43.850 align:middle line:84%
>> Most non-Western cultures,
it's assumed that if people

00:31:43.850 --> 00:31:46.480 align:middle line:84%
