00:35:43.180 --> 00:35:44.263 align:middle line:90%
but I was worried for him.

00:35:44.263 --> 00:35:47.692 align:middle line:90%
>> [SINGING] --to the sunrise.

00:35:47.692 --> 00:35:48.530 align:middle line:90%
-to the sand.

00:35:48.530 --> 00:35:52.150 align:middle line:84%
>> We started hanging out
