00:36:30.060 --> 00:36:30.330 align:middle line:10%
this.

00:36:30.330 --> 00:36:32.370 align:middle line:84%
But in that going along
process of feeling

00:36:32.370 --> 00:36:35.340 align:middle line:84%
that I was helping him, I
