00:37:01.830 --> 00:37:07.150 align:middle line:84%
>> Those openings or those
things that we call psychotic

00:37:07.150 --> 00:37:07.950 align:middle line:90%
breaks--

00:37:07.950 --> 00:37:13.770 align:middle line:84%
I think, why can't it be
