00:37:13.770 --> 00:37:17.070 align:middle line:84%
That I open to
something far greater?

00:37:17.070 --> 00:37:20.250 align:middle line:84%
That was the holy,
blessed moment

00:37:20.250 --> 00:37:24.030 align:middle line:84%
that released either
the angels or the demons

00:37:24.030 --> 00:37:30.280 align:middle line:84%
so that I could access the
deeper essence who I really am.

00:37:30.280 --> 00:37:32.630 align:middle line:84%
>> The Buddha wouldn't
have been enlightened.

00:37:32.630 --> 00:37:36.090 align:middle line:84%
Jesus wouldn't have
been Jesus without going

00:37:36.090 --> 00:37:38.490 align:middle line:90%
