00:37:38.490 --> 00:37:41.190 align:middle line:84%
There's a kind of
arc or narrative

00:37:41.190 --> 00:37:43.800 align:middle line:84%
that wants to unfold
in the psyche.

00:37:43.800 --> 00:37:48.010 align:middle line:84%
And if an individual is
given proper support,

00:37:48.010 --> 00:37:51.595 align:middle line:84%
a person can actually
reconstruct their life

00:37:51.595 --> 00:37:52.395 align:middle line:90%
at a higher level.

00:37:52.395 --> 00:37:55.000 align:middle line:90%


00:37:55.000 --> 00:37:58.370 align:middle line:84%
>> I saw a flyer
about Baltic Street.

00:37:58.370 --> 00:37:59.910 align:middle line:84%
It said it was
for people who had

00:37:59.910 --> 00:38:05.440 align:middle line:84%
experienced emotional struggle
and had mental health issues.

00:38:05.440 --> 00:38:06.240 align:middle line:90%
I went there.

00:38:06.240 --> 00:38:09.810 align:middle line:84%
I met a beautiful,
beautiful group of people.

00:38:09.810 --> 00:38:12.150 align:middle line:84%
And these people were
telling me their story

00:38:12.150 --> 00:38:15.930 align:middle line:84%
and asked me what was happening
with me and my experience.

00:38:15.930 --> 00:38:19.050 align:middle line:84%
And there I was able to
record in their studio

00:38:19.050 --> 00:38:22.010 align:middle line:84%
and get back to songwriting
and making my music.

00:38:22.010 --> 00:38:23.610 align:middle line:90%
I did some painting.

00:38:23.610 --> 00:38:25.470 align:middle line:84%
I really got in touch
with myself again.

00:38:25.470 --> 00:38:27.720 align:middle line:84%
It was like the
