00:38:38.570 --> 00:38:40.850 align:middle line:90%
for a job that was coming up.

00:38:40.850 --> 00:38:42.350 align:middle line:90%
They hired me for the position.

00:38:42.350 --> 00:38:43.860 align:middle line:90%
It was part time starting out.

00:38:43.860 --> 00:38:47.606 align:middle line:10%
And then about two months later,
