00:38:54.530 --> 00:38:56.570 align:middle line:84%
the average recovery
rate in the Western world

00:38:56.570 --> 00:38:58.730 align:middle line:84%
with all the
sophisticated diagnoses,

00:38:58.730 --> 00:39:02.670 align:middle line:84%
