00:39:36.640 --> 00:39:39.700 align:middle line:84%
or a culture that
was high paced.

00:39:39.700 --> 00:39:42.160 align:middle line:90%
I needed to move down slower.

00:39:42.160 --> 00:39:45.610 align:middle line:84%
So it was easier for me,
by being an anthropologist,

00:39:45.610 --> 00:39:47.440 align:middle line:84%
create a lifestyle
where I could be

00:39:47.440 --> 00:39:52.757 align:middle line:84%
out in villages on agricultural
time, not an industrial time.

00:39:52.757 --> 00:39:54.220 align:middle line:90%
[BLEATING]

00:39:54.220 --> 00:39:56.200 align:middle line:84%
I met a lot of people
