00:40:12.950 --> 00:40:16.750 align:middle line:84%
So when we start to lose that
connection with the environment

00:40:16.750 --> 00:40:19.330 align:middle line:84%
in a very deep way, I
think other illnesses

00:40:19.330 --> 00:40:20.215 align:middle line:90%
start to manifest.

00:40:20.215 --> 00:40:30.856 align:middle line:90%


00:40:30.856 --> 00:40:35.050 align:middle line:84%
>> [INAUDIBLE] is known as a
powerful shaman and the leader

00:40:35.050 --> 00:40:38.860 align:middle line:84%
of the [INAUDIBLE] tribe
in the Ecuadorian Amazon.

00:40:38.860 --> 00:40:42.670 align:middle line:84%
