00:40:48.240 --> 00:40:49.930 align:middle line:84%
This is somewhat
of a grass that's

00:40:49.930 --> 00:40:51.640 align:middle line:90%
growing up the trail here.

00:40:51.640 --> 00:40:54.850 align:middle line:84%
