00:41:13.462 --> 00:41:17.254 align:middle line:90%
>> [GROWLING]

00:41:17.254 --> 00:41:18.676 align:middle line:90%


00:41:18.676 --> 00:41:22.190 align:middle line:84%
>> It's a process called
shapeshifting that he uses

00:41:22.190 --> 00:41:23.630 align:middle line:90%
to guide his people.

00:41:23.630 --> 00:41:28.370 align:middle line:90%


00:41:28.370 --> 00:41:33.380 align:middle line:84%
At the time, I looked at this
with curiosity and skepticism.

00:41:33.380 --> 00:41:35.690 align:middle line:84%
Now, I wonder if
