00:42:02.120 --> 00:42:06.770 align:middle line:10%
a sensitivity that can actually
be a gift to the community.

00:42:06.770 --> 00:42:11.120 align:middle line:10%
Then, they get that person
guidance, meaning, and purpose.

00:42:11.120 --> 00:42:13.420 align:middle line:84%
I believe that's something
