00:44:27.410 --> 00:44:30.500 align:middle line:84%
And it was just
truly incredible.

00:44:30.500 --> 00:44:33.610 align:middle line:84%
These people that had
absolutely nothing

00:44:33.610 --> 00:44:36.918 align:middle line:84%
were the people that
were helping me.

