00:45:42.620 --> 00:45:44.630 align:middle line:84%
on what the symptoms of
bipolar disorder are,

00:45:44.630 --> 00:45:47.360 align:middle line:84%
for example or they would know
the symptoms of schizophrenia.

00:45:47.360 --> 00:45:49.910 align:middle line:84%
But they weren't educated
on seeing the strengths

00:45:49.910 --> 00:45:51.677 align:middle line:84%
