noticing the things

00:45:51.677 --> 00:45:53.260 align:middle line:84%
that their relative
is really great at

00:45:53.260 --> 00:45:54.650 align:middle line:90%
and pointing those out.

00:45:54.650 --> 00:45:57.514 align:middle line:84%
They weren't educated on how
to have hope for recovery.

00:45:57.514 --> 00:46:00.923 align:middle line:90%


00:46:00.923 --> 00:46:04.300 align:middle line:84%
>> There's sort of a
continuum of involvement.

00:46:04.300 --> 00:46:07.580 align:middle line:84%
There's neglect on
one end of a continuum

00:46:07.580 --> 00:46:10.880 align:middle line:84%
and then there's overprotect on
the other end of the continuum.

00:46:10.880 --> 00:46:15.020 align:middle line:84%
